{"tid":1038262,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"我師傅教我一年後，點樣由10000變成200000","createTime":"2019-02-26T14:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T14:20:03.000Z","uid":56984,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab1264424c73b2fa53833945c85d81f183b74e3","tid":1038262,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"相信各位都窮過，我都試過，好明白咩叫窮，好明白大家感受。仲記得一年前，啱啱fg，本金得10000，打份牛工先得萬零蚊，淨係搭車，食飯，保險，還學費都洗咗唔少。興趣班，咪諗啦，女朋友，算啦。養得掂自己都好好。<br />\n<br />\n我，當時只有一個願望，如果有20萬，雖然都唔多，但至少都可以食好少少，令自己係生活緊。<br />\n<br />\n我師傅見到我依排好唔對路，就問我做乜。<br />\n講一講佢背景先，佢份人好低調，都唔鐘意同人social，我點樣識佢同點解叫佢師傅就之後有機會先講，佢之前教過我點樣做一個男人，點樣看待自己人生。<br />\n<br />\n我有咩事都會同佢講，但係今次，我選擇咗沉默，窮，令我自卑，如塵埃一樣，毫不起眼。<br />\n師傅見我啲神氣唔對路，問我夜晚收工去唔去品茶？本身我都猶豫不決，因為以師傅為人，佢平時早瞓，但我見到師傅眼神，我覺得佢好似睇穿我諗乜。<br />\n<br />\n「樣子煩悶，男人，煩錢，煩女，必中其一。因何事？」<br />\n師傅講野好簡潔，同我打咁多字都未入正題，婆婆媽媽嘅性格唔同。唯有如實相告。<br />\n<br />\n師傅！窮！<br />\n<br />\n講完都覺得自己好7，面對師傅，我永遠都係似細路仔咁<br />\n，總係向佢求助。<br />\n<br />\n師傅聽完，向我介紹咗一個方法，一個價值20萬嘅方法。"},{"pid":"ae0efbb40aadd8b79e1ece8492099e183184df19","tid":1038262,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8591fac00081391ee6ee16cdb2eb0236d779f961","tid":1038262,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae0efbb40aadd8b79e1ece8492099e183184df19","tid":1038262,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1075a9448283045c6f15b7559055fee2617b8cf7","tid":1038262,"uid":72647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:13:48.000Z","msg":"買788 咪得囉，講咁多野做乜柒"},{"pid":"f3281647741dc21704e4b2ade4971764dca430fc","tid":1038262,"uid":35537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"1Q"},{"pid":"95e97878494627da47d1452c270ba94e6ae8ad35","tid":1038262,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1075a9448283045c6f15b7559055fee2617b8cf7","tid":1038262,"uid":72647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:13:48.000Z","msg":"買788 咪得囉，講咁多野做乜柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"屌，咁快講答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df38917cdad796c3d25ee6a2158c304659f7b29","tid":1038262,"uid":187753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"麵包 A、 B、 C、 D邊個係苦嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b429a91279f8244d62803abf41a84aca448b74","tid":1038262,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df38917cdad796c3d25ee6a2158c304659f7b29","tid":1038262,"uid":187753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"麵包 A、 B、 C、 D邊個係苦嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"唔想知，走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c02775ac8f5a72ed2e41cbc16f116ef2af4f51","tid":1038262,"uid":238193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"我師傳教我20變25000000<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D66ZWiIsdiM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD66ZWiIsdiM&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6Q5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=037a51d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D66ZWiIsdiM</a>"}]}